data.description: Location, location, location! This West Ashley home is close to everything! Less than 10 mins to downtown Charleston. 15 mins to the airport and 20 mins to Folly Beach! lots of shops, restaurants, and groceries stores, mins to MUSC. Plus, this charming property is located in an established, peaceful, quiet, family-friendly neighborhood. Even with no HOA. This charming 3 bedrooms 2 baths home you will find a opened living room dining room combo, with master suite on The main floor, two additional bedrooms upstairs. Front porch, to enjoy with a cup of coffee, huge backyard to entertain and gardening. This home need some TLC. This home you can built up sweat equity. This home can be owner occupied or an investment property. This property is being SOLD AS IS!!
